trans-unit.source: Allows programmatic access to the HTML <xref uid="langword_csharp_<title>" name="<title>" href=""></xref> element on the server.
trans-unit.target: Tillater programmatisk tilgang til HTML <xref uid="langword_csharp_<title>" name="<title>" href=""> </xref> element på serveren.

trans-unit.source: Use the HtmlTitle class to programmatically specify the HTML `<title>` element of a Web Forms page.
trans-unit.target: Bruk klassen HtmlTitle til å angi programmatisk HTML `<title>` element av et webskjema-siden.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > You can also set the page title by using the `title` attribute of the [@ Page](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/f06cf9e5-22bb-461d-8b8f-549e53ff40a4) directive, or by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.Title%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Du kan også angi tittelen på siden ved hjelp av `title` for den [@ siden](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/f06cf9e5-22bb-461d-8b8f-549e53ff40a4) direktivet, eller ved å angi <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.Title%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Page> </xref:System.Web.UI.Page.Title%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to create and initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle> control using default values.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å opprette og starte en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle>kontrollere bruker standardverdier.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle>

trans-unit.source: It creates an HTML `<title>` element on the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Det opprettes et HTML `<title>` element på siden.

trans-unit.source: The following table shows the initial property value for an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle> class.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser første egenskapsverdien for en forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle>

trans-unit.source: |Property|Initial Value| |--------------|-------------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlControl.TagName%2A>|The "title" literal string.|
trans-unit.target: | Egenskapen | Standardverdi | |--------------|-------------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlControl.TagName%2A>| "Tittel" strenglitteral. |</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlControl.TagName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Notifies the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle"></xref> control that an XML or HTML element was parsed and adds that element to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> collection of the control.
trans-unit.target: Varsler den <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle"> </xref> kontroll som et XML- eller HTML-element ble analysert, og legger til dette elementet til den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> -samlingen i kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: If the element added to the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle> control is a <xref:System.Web.UI.LiteralControl> control, then the AddParsedSubObject method sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle.Text%2A> property with the value of the literal string; otherwise, the base <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.AddParsedSubObject%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: Hvis elementet er lagt til i <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle>kontrollen er en <xref:System.Web.UI.LiteralControl>kontrollen, og deretter AddParsedSubObject metoden angir den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle.Text%2A>egenskapen med verdien for strenglitteral; ellers grunntallet <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.AddParsedSubObject%2A>-metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.AddParsedSubObject%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle.Text%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.LiteralControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle>

trans-unit.source: The AddParsedSubObject method is used primarily by control developers extending the functionality of the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle> control.
trans-unit.target: Metoden AddParsedSubObject brukes hovedsakelig av kontrollutviklere utvide funksjonaliteten til de <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that represents the parsed element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>som representerer elementet analysere.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> collection for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> samling for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> object to contain the current server control's child server controls.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> objektet som inneholder den gjeldende serverkontroll underordnede serverkontroller.

trans-unit.source: Renders the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle"></xref> control to the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Gjengivelser av <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle"> </xref> kontrollen til den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The Render method first calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.RenderBeginTag%2A> method using the `Title` member of the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Gjengivelse metoden første kall den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.RenderBeginTag%2A>metoden ved hjelp av den `Title` medlem av den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag>opplisting.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag> </xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.RenderBeginTag%2A>

trans-unit.source: Next, any child controls of the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle> control are rendered.
trans-unit.target: Neste andre underordnede kontrollerer av den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle>kontrollen gjengis.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTitle>

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.RenderEndTag%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: Til slutt i <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.RenderEndTag%2A>-metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter.RenderEndTag%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"></xref> that contains the output stream to render on the client.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"> </xref> som inneholder utdata dataflyten å gjengi på klienten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the text of the HTML <xref uid="langword_csharp_<title>" name="<title>" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir teksten for HTML <xref uid="langword_csharp_<title>" name="<title>" href=""> </xref> elementet.

trans-unit.source: Use the Text property to specify or determine the title of the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Bruk Text-egenskapen til å angi eller fastslå tittelen på websiden.

trans-unit.source: The text of the HTML <xref uid="langword_csharp_<title>" name="<title>" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Teksten i HTML <xref uid="langword_csharp_<title>" name="<title>" href=""> </xref> elementet.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").
